            <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 lg:w-1/4 text-center p-2">
                <div class="bg-gray-200 border rounded p-4 flex flex-col justify-center h-full">
                    <div class="text-gray-600">Total donors</div>
                    <div class="text-2xl font-bold">
                        {{ num_donors | thousands }}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 lg:w-1/4 text-center p-2">
                <div class="bg-gray-200 border rounded p-4 flex flex-col justify-center h-full">
                    <div class="text-gray-600">Total £ raised</div>
                    <div class="text-2xl font-bold">
                        £{{ money_raised | thousands }}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 lg:w-1/4 text-center p-2">
                <div class="bg-gray-200 border rounded p-4 flex flex-col justify-center h-full">
                    <div class="text-gray-600">Fundraiser donations</div>
                    <div class="text-2xl font-bold">
                        TODO
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 lg:w-1/4 text-center p-2">
                <div class="bg-gray-200 border rounded p-4 flex flex-col justify-center h-full">
                    <div class="text-gray-600">£ left to raise</div>
                    <div class="text-2xl font-bold">
                        TODO
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    {{ centreQuote(
        "We are grateful - every day - for all those on the front line, the doctors, the nurses, the porters and everyone working so hard to help patients recover and to keep us all well.",
        "Marie-Helene, May 2020") }}

    <div class="py-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row mx-auto md:justify-center">
        <div class="md:px-2 flex justify-center">
            <a class="dbox-donation-button bg-blue-800 hover:bg-blue-900 transition-all ease-in-out duration-300 py-4 px-6 rounded-lg cursor-pointer text-white text-lg md:text-2xl flex justify-center items-center font-regular border-b-4 border-blue-900" href="/donor-wall">
                See our Donor Wall of ❤️
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container md:w-4/5 mx-auto px-4 py-6 md:pb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold pb-2">How can you help?</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap pb-4">
            <div class="w-full lg:w-1/3 text-center p-2">
                <div class="rounded bg-gray-200 p-4 flex flex-col h-full">
                    <h3 class="text-xl mb-2">1. Donate today</h3>
                    <p class="text-base">It costs just £6 to provide a hot meal to an NHS worker and support a local business at the same time.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full lg:w-1/3 text-center p-2">
                <div class="rounded bg-gray-200 p-4 flex flex-col h-full">
                    <h3 class="text-xl mb-2">2. Fundraise</h3>
                    <p class="text-base">Do something fun (virtually) to raise money for meals. Check out some fundraisers for inspiration and start one of your own.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full lg:w-1/3 text-center p-2">
                <div class="rounded bg-gray-200 p-4 flex flex-col h-full">
                    <h3 class="text-xl mb-2">3. Spread the word</h3>
                    <p class="text-base">Shout from the rooftops/your window/balcony. Just #StayInside and spread the word to your friends and family</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="md:w-4/5 lg:w-2/3 mx-auto py-6 md:pb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-center md:text-4xl font-bold pb-2">
            NEED SOMETHING ABOUT THE GAP
        </h2>
        <div class="pt-2 flex flex-col md:flex-row mx-auto md:justify-center flex-shrink">
            <div class="py-2 md:px-2 flex justify-center">
                <a class="bg-blue-600 text-white hover:bg-blue-800 border-b-2 border-blue-800 transition-all ease-in-out duration-300 py-3 px-5 md:py-4 md:px-6 rounded cursor-pointer text-xl leading-tight" href="/fundraising">
                    Start fundraising
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="py-2 md:px-2 flex justify-center">
                <a class="bg-blue-600 text-white hover:bg-blue-800 border-b-2 border-blue-800 transition-all ease-in-out duration-300 py-3 px-5 md:py-4 md:px-6 rounded cursor-pointer text-xl leading-tight" href="/campaigns">
                    Partner
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="py-2 md:px-2 flex justify-center">
                <a class="bg-blue-600 text-white hover:bg-blue-800 border-b-2 border-blue-800 transition-all ease-in-out duration-300 py-3 px-5 md:py-4 md:px-6 rounded cursor-pointer text-xl leading-tight" href="/campaigns">
                    Donate now
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-lg text-center md:text-xl text-gray-700">
            We have partnered with a UK registered charity to act as a fiscal sponsor for larger donations. If you would like to speak to someone from the team please get in touch here.
        </p>
    </div>

